		<titleShort>clairvoyant</titleShort>
		<slot>Childhood</slot>
		<baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef] always seemed to know more about the world than [PAWN_pronoun] should have, at [PAWN_possessive] age. Many villagefolk claimed that [PAWN_pronoun] was a messenger from above, and requested [PAWN_possessive] insight into their futures.</baseDesc>
		<bodyTypeMale>Thin</bodyTypeMale>
		<bodyTypeFemale>Thin</bodyTypeFemale>
		<spawnCategories>
			<li>SatyrandFaun</li>
			<li>SatyrWild</li>
			<li>FaunWild</li>
		</spawnCategories>
